    public interface SF
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'SF'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Number
    • Offset
    • Id
    • Length
    • Children
    • Raw Data
    • Charset

    See Also:
    BasePackage.getSF()
